# Distillery env fallback for secrets.
#
# The primary secret source is the TinyCloud secrets vault
# (secrets.tinycloud.xyz, "secrets" space, key "secrets/<NAME>").
# Until the headless vault transport lands — and on machines without it —
# skills fall back to env vars.
#
# Gemini key: any ONE of these works (checked in this order, mirroring
# pulse-radio's resolveGeminiKey precedence):
GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY=
# GEMINI_API_KEY=
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=

# Example local corpus (NEVER hardcoded in skills — transcript paths are
# always passed as invocation arguments):
# "/Users/hunterhorsfall/Obsidian Vaults/TinyCloud 2025/Team Relays/TinyCloud Team Space/Fireflies-Transcripts"
